	<h1 class="title">「这世界」章鱼进化程度高成这样？只能用外星人才说得通啊</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-14 14:15:06 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13521/medium/13521.jpg?1439525687" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13521" data-title="《「这世界」章鱼进化程度高成这样？只能用外星人才说得通啊》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13521/medium/13521.jpg?1439525687" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13521.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
